{
  "stem": "802.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And in some way, ironically, even though this was a form of dehumanization, it helped us because nobody knew that my mother, my sister, and I were related to each other because they would've definitely separated us.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we used to dig the potatoes and sit very close to each other.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then we also carried grass, you know, strips of grass, from one place the other.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In addition to that, there was a huge crater in Majdanek.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was outside of the camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now, my sister-- my mother, my sister, and I tried never to be separated.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But sometimes we had no choice.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So one day, my mother was made to stay on the campgrounds, and my sister and I were made to go to this huge crater.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was really enormous.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in that crater-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I'm trying to give you more or less the dimensions-- maybe like a small baseball field.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I'm not too familiar with baseball, so I don't know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyway, it was huge.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was not terribly deep.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But in it were all kinds of human possessions, Jewish human possessions-- hair, teeth, you know, bridges, eyeglasses, books-- lots of books-- and various kinds of cloth articles.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But-- but they were piled up in separate piles.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was working there with my sister.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were putting-- we were making some order because for the Germans, [GERMAN], which means, 'there must be order.'",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we were putting these eyeglasses together in one pile, the underwear together, the outerwear, the shoes, the books, whatever else.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was a woman next to me-- my sister was working at another pile.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "As I said, we tried not to be separated, but sometimes they assigned us to these things.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
